{"type":"message","id":"20627eb0","parentId":"0cf66ab9","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:32:15.683Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_17bdd49b07e74a7bb12b6d4d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nsrc/config_paths.py - Portable 动态路径管理\n\n所有路径相对于主程序目录 (APP_DIR)，支持 PyInstaller 打包。\nPortable 应用规范：整个程序是 Portable 应用，所有路径相对于主程序目录。\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport warnings\nwarnings.warn(\n    \"src/config_paths.py is deprecated. Use 'src/main/core/config_merger.py' instead. \"\n    \"Will be removed in a future version.\",\n    DeprecationWarning,\n    stacklevel=2,\n)\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n\ndef get_app_dir() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取主程序所在目录（支持 PyInstaller 打包）。\n\n    开发模式: 返回 src/ 的父目录（即项目根目录）\n    PyInstaller 模式: 返回可执行文件所在目录 (dist/AstroHub/)\n    \"\"\"\n    if getattr(sys, 'frozen', False):\n        return Path(sys.executable).parent\n    return Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent\n\n\ndef get_meipass_dir() -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"获取 PyInstaller 运行时临时目录（仅打包模式可用）。\"\"\"\n    if getattr(sys, 'frozen', False) and hasattr(sys, '_MEIPASS'):\n        return Path(sys._MEIPASS)\n    return None\n\n\ndef get_sdk_root() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取 SDK 参考路径（仅开发模式回退用）。\n\n    开发模式：基于 APP_DIR 的相对路径 APP_DIR/ref/HIK SDK/...\n    Portable 模式：基于程序所在目录 ../ref/HIK SDK/...\n    \"\"\"\n    if getattr(sys, 'frozen', False):\n        # Portable 模式：可执行文件所在目录为基准\n        exe_dir = Path(sys.executable).parent\n        return exe_dir / 'ref' / 'HIK SDK' / 'HCSadpSDKV4.2.8.10_build20220517_Win64_ZH_20231201161210' / 'HCSadpSDKV4.2.8.10_build20220517_Win64_ZH' / 'libs'\n    # 开发模式：项目根目录的 ref/ 目录\n    return get_app_dir() / 'ref' / 'HIK SDK' / 'HCSadpSDKV4.2.8.10_build20220517_Win64_ZH_20231201161210' / 'HCSadpSDKV4.2.8.10_build20220517_Win64_ZH' / 'libs'\n\n\n# ============================================================\n# 应用根目录\n# ============================================================\nAPP_DIR = get_app_dir()\n\n# ============================================================\n# 数据目录 (全部基于 APP_DIR/data/)\n# ============================================================\nDATA_DIR = APP_DIR / 'data'\nLOG_DIR = APP_DIR / 'log'\nCONFIG_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'config'\nDB_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'db'\nRECORD_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'records'\nREPORT_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'reports'\nDOWNLOAD_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'downloads'\nHLS_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'hls'\nCALIBRATION_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'calibration'\n\n# v6.03: 新数据结构路径\nSYSTEM_FILE = DATA_DIR / 'system.json'       # 本机系统信息\nREGISTRY_FILE = DATA_DIR / 'registry.json'   # 设备注册表\nDEVICES_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'devices'           # 设备数据目录\n\n# ============================================================\n# DLL 路径 (SADP)\n# ============================================================\n# 开发模式下 SDK libs 目录\nSDK_LIBS_DIR = get_sdk_root()\n\n# ============================================================\n# 所有需要创建的目录列表\n# ============================================================\nALL_DATA_DIRS = [\n    DATA_DIR,\n    LOG_DIR,\n    CONFIG_DIR,\n    DB_DIR,\n    RECORD_DIR,\n    REPORT_DIR,\n    DOWNLOAD_DIR,\n    HLS_DIR,\n    CALIBRATION_DIR,\n    DEVICES_DIR,\n]\n\n\ndef ensure_directories() -> None:\n    \"\"\"确保所有运行时目录存在（首次运行自动创建）。\"\"\"\n    for directory in ALL_DATA_DIRS:\n        directory.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n\n# ============================================================\n# PyInstaller 静态资源路径\n# ============================================================\n\ndef get_web_dir() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取 web 静态资源目录。\"\"\"\n    meipass = get_meipass_dir()\n    if meipass:\n        return meipass / 'src' / 'web'\n    return Path(__file__).resolve().parent / 'web'\n\n\ndef get_index_html() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取 index.html 路径。\"\"\"\n    return get_web_dir() / 'index.html'\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781332335683}}
{"type":"message","id":"407b6c5f","parentId":"20627eb0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:32:39.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`config_paths.py` 还存在，只是被标记为 deprecated。问题是：\n\n1. **设备列表为空**: `ptz_manager.py` 的 `list_stored_devices` 依赖 `config.load_ptz_config()`，而 `ConfigManager.load_ptz_config()` 读取的是 `devices/{mac}/info.json`，但格式可能与 `registry.json` 不匹配\n\n2. **ISAPI 断开后仍连接**: `disconnect_device` 只清除了 `_controllers`，但 WASM 登出可能未执行\n\n3. **画面控制下拉菜单未加载**: 前端 `loadDeviceImageParams` 函数可能有问题\n\n让我先备份，然后修复这些问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e5023c2071724b8ebbc18c4158c05a9c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"xcopy \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\" \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\backup_20260613_143000\\src\" /E /I /Q","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108388,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108622,"cost":{"input":0.108388,"output":0.0007488000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10913679999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332335684,"responseId":"cht000da861@dx19ebfae8e5cba5e412"}}
