{"type":"message","id":"160d810a","parentId":"4eee762c","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:35:52.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有 `function.json` 文件！这就是问题所在。用户从未运行过功能探测，所以没有缓存文件。\n\n**问题分析**：\n\n1. **设备列表为空**: 因为 `load_ptz_config()` 遍历 `devices/{mac}/info.json`，需要确认是否正确读取\n2. **画面控制下拉菜单未加载**: 因为 `function.json` 不存在，API 返回失败\n\n让我检查前端在 `function.json` 不存在时的行为："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_69e7483d8e324d9e80969e40","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":390,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129393,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129539,"cost":{"input":0.129393,"output":0.0004672,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1298602}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332518795,"responseId":"cht000db8b8@dx19ebfb180b5b8ab282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e3dbcc4","parentId":"160d810a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:35:52.022Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_69e7483d8e324d9e80969e40","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v6.14: 使用 async/await 确保顺序但不阻塞 UI\n    (async function() {\n        try {\n            // 先加载 function.json\n            var r = await apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function');\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n                deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n                console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded');\n            }\n        } catch (e) {\n            console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json failed:', e);\n        }\n        \n        // 然后加载其他参数（顺序执行但不阻塞）\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    })();\n}\n\n// 加载 OSD 状态\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\n    // PTZ OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\n            // 保存到 localStorage\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            // 从 localStorage 读取上次设置\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // Info OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n}\n\nfunction updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled) {\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOn');\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOff');\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\n        if (enabled) {\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n        } else {\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n\n[526 more lines in file. Use offset=470 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781332552022}}
