{"type":"message","id":"4fb20fe3","parentId":"abe6ae8e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:40:32.655Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"34066\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 14:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n先修复以下工作\n1. 没有json文件，就直接将这部分设定为不可用，整个画面控制这部分都是不可用的，灰色无法操作状态，点击操作，需要有文字提示说明（请先完成功能测试）\n2. 其他路径按照你检查的结果修复\n3. 当JSON文件明确没有需要的端点时，需要显示灰色不可操作，并且文字提示，设备不支持该功能\n现在给我完整梳理逻辑流程，我需要看到，具体的，读什么路径的什么文件\n1. 初次发现设备\n2. 断开设备的流程\n3. 快速连接-重启PC或关闭程序"}],"timestamp":1781332832649}}
{"type":"message","id":"3055ccb0","parentId":"4fb20fe3","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:40:48.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来梳理完整逻辑流程，然后开始修复。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 逻辑流程梳理\n\n### 1. 初次发现设备\n\n```\n用户点击\"发现设备\"\n    ↓\n前端: apiGet('/api/v1/discovery/sadp')\n    ↓\n后端: SADP 多播发现 → 返回设备列表\n    ↓\n前端: refreshDevices() → apiGet('/api/v1/devices')\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.list_devices() \n    ↓\n    ├── list_stored_devices() → 读取 data/devices/{mac}/info.json\n    ├── get_discovered_devices() → 内存缓存（SADP发现）\n    └── 合并去重返回\n    ↓\n前端: renderDevices() 显示设备列表\n```\n\n**文件读写**:\n| 操作 | 文件路径 |\n|------|----------|\n| 读取存储设备 | `data/devices/{mac}/info.json` |\n| 读取注册表 | `data/registry.json` |\n\n---\n\n### 2. 断开设备流程\n\n```\n用户点击\"断开\"\n    ↓\n前端: disconnectDevice(ip)\n    ├── stopPtzPositionPoll() - 停止位置轮询\n    ├── wasmLogout() - WASM 登出视频流\n    ├── updateWasmStatus('disconnected')\n    └── apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/disconnect')\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.disconnect_device(ip)\n    ├── 从 _controllers 移除\n    ├── 从 _clients 移除\n    └── 更新 info.json (connected: false)\n    ↓\n前端:\n    ├── window.connectedDevice = null\n    ├── refreshDevices() - 刷新设备列表\n    ├── refreshPtzDeviceList() - 刷新PTZ下拉\n    └── refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors() - 刷新高级功能下拉\n```\n\n**文件读写**:\n| 操作 | 文件路径 |\n|------|----------|\n| 更新连接状态 | `data/devices/{mac}/info.json` (connected: false) |\n| 更新注册表 | `data/registry.json` (active_device: \"\") |\n\n---\n\n### 3. 快速连接 - 重启PC或关闭程序\n\n```\n程序启动 / 页面加载\n    ↓\n前端: \n    ├── 自动调用 quickConnect(true) 或\n    ├── 调用 restoreConnectionState()\n    ↓\n前端: apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/connected')\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.get_connected_device()\n    ↓\n    ├── 读取 registry.json → active_device (MAC)\n    ├── 读取 data/devices/{mac}/info.json → 设备信息\n    └── 检查 _controllers 是否有该设备\n    ↓\n返回: {success: true, device: {ip, mac, ...}}\n    ↓\n前端:\n    ├── 有设备 → 自动调用 connectDevice(ip)\n    └── 无设备 → 显示\"无上次连接设备\"\n```\n\n**文件读写**:\n| 操作 | 文件路径 |\n|------|----------|\n| 读取活跃设备 | `data/registry.json` (active_device) |\n| 读取设备详情 | `data/devices/{mac}/info.json` |\n\n---\n\n### 4. 画面控制加载流程\n\n```\n设备连接成功\n    ↓\n前端: loadDeviceImageParams(ip)\n    ↓\n    ├── apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + ip + '/function') → 读取 function.json\n    │   └── 成功: deviceFunctionData = r.data\n    │   └── 失败: deviceFunctionData = null\n    ↓\n    ├── loadWhiteBalance(ip) → apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + ip + '/image/whitebalance')\n    ├── loadShutter(ip) → apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + ip + '/image/shutter')\n    ├── loadIris(ip) → apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + ip + '/image/iris')\n    └── ... 其他参数\n```\n\n**文件读写**:\n| 操作 | 文件路径 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 读取功能探测结果 | `data/devices/{mac}/function.json` | **不存在时画面控制不可用** |\n| ISAPI 实时读取 | `/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance` 等 | 需要 function.json 验证支持 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 修复计划\n\n现在开始修复：\n\n1. **画面控制：无 function.json 时显示灰色不可用**\n2. **修复 get_device_function API 路径**\n3. **断开设备后清除 registry.json 的 active_device**\n4. **快速连接：正确读取 registry.json**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5942b7b50fec46b98765d629","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":150,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108325,"output":1042,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109367,"cost":{"input":0.10832499999999999,"output":0.0033344000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11165939999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332832656,"responseId":"cht000defe6@dx19ebfb5f83dba5b442"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b4b1dd9","parentId":"3055ccb0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:40:48.069Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5942b7b50fec46b98765d629","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-console\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size:18px;margin-bottom:8px\">主控台</h2>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px\">\n                <div class=\"status-item\">\n                    <span class=\"status-dot red\" id=\"deviceDot\"></span>\n                    <span id=\"deviceStatus\">未连接</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"ptzControlArea\">\n                <!-- 左右布局: 左控制, 中间画面+媒体, 右日志+画面控制 -->\n                <div class=\"console-layout\">\n                    <!-- 左: PTZ控制（整合：指向+预置点+变焦/对焦） -->\n                    <div class=\"console-left\">\n                        <!-- PTZ控制（折叠） -->\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section collapsed\" id=\"ptzControlSection\">\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('ptzControlSection')\">\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">🎯 PTZ控制</h3>\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\n                                <!-- 指向控制 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">指向</div>\n                                <div class=\"ptz-controls\">\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up')\">↑</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('left')\">←</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn center\">●</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('right')\">→</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-left')\">↙</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down')\">↓</button>\n                                    <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-right')\">↘</button>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"ptz-speed\">\n                                    <label>速度:</label>\n                                    <input type=\"range\" id=\"ptzSpeed\" min=\"1\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\">\n                                    <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\">50</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-top:8px\">\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning\" onclick=\"ptzStop()\">停止</button>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"ptz-position\" id=\"ptzPosition\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">\n                                    Pan: -- | Tilt: -- | Zoom: --\n                                </div>\n                                <!-- 预置点 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">预置点</div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <select id=\"ptzPresetSelect\" style=\"padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px;min-width:120px\">\n                                        <option value=\"\">选择预置点</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzGotoSelectedPreset()\">前往</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzSetSelectedPreset()\">保存</button>\n                                </div>\n                                <div id=\"ptzPresetResult\" style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\"></div>\n                                <!-- 变焦/对焦 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">变焦/对焦</div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">焦距:</span>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍+</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍-</button>\n                                </div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">对焦:</span>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\n                                    <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\n                                        <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n                                        <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n                                        <option value=\"semiauto\">半自动</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- 跟踪控制 -->\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"trackControlSection\">\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('trackControlSection')\">\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#f0883e;margin:0\">🛤 跟踪控制</h3>\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" id=\"btnTrackSidereal\" onclick=\"setTracking('trackSidereal')\">恒星跟踪</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" id=\"btnTrackLunar\" onclick=\"setTracking('trackLunar')\">月球跟踪</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" id=\"btnTrackSolar\" onclick=\"setTracking('trackSolar')\">太阳跟踪</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-danger\" id=\"btnTrackOff\" onclick=\"setTracking('trackOff')\">关闭跟踪</button>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- 中: 实时画面 + 媒体操作 -->\n                    <div class=\"console-center\">\n                        <!-- 实时画面 -->\n                        <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3fb950;margin:0 0 8px\">📺 实时画面</h3>\n                        <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;width:100%;\">\n                            <div id=\"divPlugin\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;display:block;background:#000;\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- 媒体操作（折叠，整合Live Stack + 码流） -->\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section collapsed\" id=\"mediaControlSection\">\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaControlSection')\">\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3fb950;margin:0\">📷 媒体操作</h3>\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px\">\n                                    <!-- 码流选择 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;justify-content:center\">\n                                        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">码流:</span>\n                                        <select id=\"streamType\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"changeStreamType(this.value)\">\n                                            <option value=\"1\">主码流</option>\n                                            <option value=\"2\" selected>子码流</option>\n                                            <option value=\"3\">第三码流</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 截图/录像 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnConsoleSnapshot\" onclick=\"consoleSnapshot()\">📷 截图</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" id=\"btnConsoleRecordStart\" onclick=\"consoleRecordStart()\">⏺ 录像</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnConsoleRecordStop\" onclick=\"consoleRecordStop()\" disabled>⏹ 停止</button>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"consoleRecordStatus\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\">未录像</div>\n                                    <!-- Live Stack -->\n                                    <div class=\"section-subtitle\">Live Stack 实时叠加</div>\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"off\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('off')\">关闭</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"2s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('2s')\">2s</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"5s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('5s')\">5s</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"10s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('10s')\">10s</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"30s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('30s')\">30s</button>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                        硬件曝光: <input type=\"number\" id=\"hardwareExposureMs\" value=\"100\" style=\"width:60px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\"> ms\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"btn-group\" style=\"justify-content:center\">\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStart\" onclick=\"startLiveStack()\">▶ 开始</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStop\" onclick=\"stopLiveStack()\" disabled>⏹ 停止</button>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-success btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackSave\" onclick=\"saveLiveStack()\" disabled>💾 保存</button>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div id=\"liveStackStatus\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\">叠加: 关闭</div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- 右: 操作日志 + 画面控制 -->\n                    <div class=\"console-right\">\n                        <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0 0 8px\">📋 操作日志</h3>\n                        <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;flex:1;overflow-y:auto;max-height:200px\">\n                            <div id=\"ptzLogBox\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\n                                <div style=\"color:#6e7681\">等待连接...</div>\n                            </div>\n\n[845 more lines in file. Use offset=151 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781332848069}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c5a51c1","parentId":"8b4b1dd9","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:41:00.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我继续读取画面控制部分："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-89025871709b4f7aabee1dfaa4f48c43","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":150,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":112083,"output":52,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112135,"cost":{"input":0.11208299999999999,"output":0.0001664,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11224939999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332848070,"responseId":"cht000ddd53@dx19ebfb633d0ba5a412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c2b4631","parentId":"6c5a51c1","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:41:00.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-89025871709b4f7aabee1dfaa4f48c43","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- 画面控制（折叠，移到右侧） -->\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section collapsed\" id=\"imageControlSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('imageControlSection')\">\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#d29922;margin:0\">🎨 画面控制</h3>\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\n                                <div class=\"card\">\n                                    <!-- 基础调节 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">亮度 <span id=\"brightnessVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleBrightness\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('brightnessVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('brightness', this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对比度 <span id=\"contrastVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleContrast\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('contrastVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('contrast', this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 饱和度 + 锐度 - v6.02: 合并同一行 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">饱和度 <span id=\"saturationVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleSaturation\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('saturationVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('saturation', this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">锐度 <span id=\"sharpnessVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleSharpness\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('sharpnessVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setSharpness(this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 白平衡 -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡模式</label>\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceMode(this.value)\">\n                                            <option value=\"\">-- 加载中 --</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#f85149\">R <span id=\"wbRedVal\" style=\"color:#f85149\">--</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbRed\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbRedVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('red', this.value)\" disabled>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#58a6ff\">B <span id=\"wbBlueVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbBlue\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbBlueVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', this.value)\" disabled>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 降噪 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">空域降噪 <span id=\"dnrSpatialVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrSpatial\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrSpatialVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('spatial', this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">时域降噪 <span id=\"dnrTemporalVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrTemporal\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrTemporalVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('temporal', this.value)\">\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 (v5.47: 整合到一行) -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">曝光模式</label>\n                                        <select id=\"exposureMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setExposureMode(this.value);updateShutterIrisState()\">\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 快门/光圈整合一行 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">快门</label>\n                                            <select id=\"shutterSpeed\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setShutterSpeed(this.value)\" disabled>\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\n                                            </select>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">光圈</label>\n                                            <select id=\"irisLevel\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setIris(this.value)\" disabled>\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\n                                            </select>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- OSD 控制 - v6.14: 标题改为“信息” -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:12px;margin:0\">信息</label>\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px\">\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n                                                <span style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">OSD</span>\n                                                <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n                                                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n                                                    <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n                                                </label>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n                                                <span style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">PTZ</span>\n                                                <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n                                                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n                                                    <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n                                                </label>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n<style>\n/* v6.02: 拨杆开关样式 */\n.toggle-switch {\n    position: relative;\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 22px;\n}\n.toggle-switch input {\n    opacity: 0;\n    width: 0;\n    height: 0;\n}\n.toggle-slider {\n    position: absolute;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    background-color: #30363d;\n    transition: 0.3s;\n    border-radius: 22px;\n}\n.toggle-slider:before {\n    position: absolute;\n    content: \"\";\n    height: 16px;\n    width: 16px;\n    left: 3px;\n    bottom: 3px;\n    background-color: #e0e6f0;\n    transition: 0.3s;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n}\ninput:checked + .toggle-slider {\n    background-color: #238636;\n}\ninput:checked + .toggle-slider:before {\n    transform: translateX(18px);\n}\n\n/* 折叠面板样式 */\n.collapsible-section {\n    background: #161b22;\n    border: 1px solid #21262d;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n}\n.collapsible-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 10px 12px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    background: #0d1117;\n    transition: background 0.2s;\n}\n.collapsible-header:hover {\n    background: #161b22;\n}\n.collapse-icon {\n    color: #8b949e;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\n}\n.collapsible-section.collapsed .collapse-icon {\n    transform: rotate(-90deg);\n}\n.collapsible-content {\n    padding: 12px;\n    max-height: 1000px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out, padding 0.3s;\n}\n.collapsible-section.collapsed .collapsible-content {\n    max-height: 0;\n    padding: 0 12px;\n}\n.section-subtitle {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #6e7681;\n    margin: 8px 0 4px;\n    padding-top: 8px;\n    border-top: 1px solid #21262d;\n}\n.section-subtitle:first-child {\n    border-top: none;\n\n[646 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781332860071}}
{"type":"message","id":"d143dc3b","parentId":"4c2b4631","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:41:10.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我理解了画面控制的结构。让我修改：\n\n1. 添加 `disableImageControls()` 函数 - 无 function.json 时禁用所有控件\n2. 修改 `loadDeviceImageParams()` - 检测缓存后决定是否启用控件\n3. 添加提示文字"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5a6e5d31e15044b89e4a7a3c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":380,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":128721,"output":105,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128826,"cost":{"input":0.128721,"output":0.00033600000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.129057}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332860072,"responseId":"cht000df502@dx19ebfb66044ba5b442"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4717a10","parentId":"d143dc3b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:41:10.148Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5a6e5d31e15044b89e4a7a3c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n// 连接设备时加载图像参数（从function.json读取范围，从ISAPI读取当前值）\nfunction loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v6.14: 使用 async/await 确保顺序但不阻塞 UI\n    (async function() {\n        try {\n            // 先加载 function.json\n            var r = await apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function');\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n                deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n                console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded');\n            }\n        } catch (e) {\n            console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json failed:', e);\n        }\n        \n        // 然后加载其他参数（顺序执行但不阻塞）\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    })();\n}\n\n// 加载 OSD 状态\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\n    // PTZ OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\n            // 保存到 localStorage\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            // 从 localStorage 读取上次设置\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // Info OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n}\n\nfunction updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled) {\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOn');\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOff');\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\n        if (enabled) {\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n        } else {\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\n        }\n    }\n    // v6.14: 同步开关状态\n    var sw = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitch');\n    if (sw) sw.checked = enabled;\n}\n\nfunction updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled) {\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOn');\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOff');\n\n[516 more lines in file. Use offset=480 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781332870148}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a220169","parentId":"f4717a10","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:41:41.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我来修改 `console.html`，添加禁用逻辑和提示："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99a5d691c0904723a27981dc","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"\n// v6.20: 功能支持状态\nvar deviceFunctionData = null;\nvar functionCacheLoaded = false;\n\n// v6.20: 禁用画面控制所有控件\nfunction disableImageControls(reason) {\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel',\n        'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitch'\n    ];\n    controls.forEach(function(id) {\n        var el = document.getElementById(id);\n        if (el) {\n            el.disabled = true;\n            el.style.opacity = '0.5';\n            el.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // 显示提示文字\n    var section = document.getElementById('imageControlSection');\n    if (section) {\n        var content = section.querySelector('.collapsible-content');\n        if (content && !document.getElementById('functionCacheWarning')) {\n            var warning = document.createElement('div');\n            warning.id = 'functionCacheWarning';\n            warning.style.cssText = 'background:#4a3a1a;border:1px solid #d29922;border-radius:6px;padding:12px;margin:8px 0;color:#d29922;font-size:12px;text-align:center';\n            warning.innerHTML = '<strong>⚠️ ' + reason + '</strong><br><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">请在「高级功能 → 功能探测」中完成测试</span>';\n            content.insertBefore(warning, content.firstChild);\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// v6.20: 启用画面控制\nfunction enableImageControls() {\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel',\n        'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitch'\n    ];\n    controls.forEach(function(id) {\n        var el = document.getElementById(id);\n        if (el) {\n            el.disabled = false;\n            el.style.opacity = '1';\n            el.style.cursor = 'pointer';\n        }\n    });\n    \n    // 移除警告\n    var warning = document.getElementById('functionCacheWarning');\n    if (warning) warning.remove();\n}\n\n// 连接设备时加载图像参数（从function.json读取范围，从ISAPI读取当前值）\n// v6.20: 优先读取缓存，无缓存时禁用控件\nfunction loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v6.20: 重置状态\n    functionCacheLoaded = false;\n    deviceFunctionData = null;\n    \n    // v6.20: 使用 async/await 确保顺序但不阻塞 UI\n    (async function() {\n        // 1. 先尝试加载 function.json 缓存\n        try {\n            var r = await apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function');\n            if (r && r.success && r.data && r.data.results) {\n                deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n                functionCacheLoaded = true;\n                console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded from cache');\n                enableImageControls();\n            } else {\n                console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json not found or invalid');\n                disableImageControls('未完成功能测试');\n                functionCacheLoaded = false;\n                return; // 无缓存，不加载其他参数\n            }\n        } catch (e) {\n            console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json failed:', e);\n            disableImageControls('未完成功能测试');\n            functionCacheLoaded = false;\n            return;\n        }\n        \n        // 2. 有缓存才加载其他参数（顺序执行但不阻塞）\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    })();\n}","oldText":"\n// 连接设备时加载图像参数（从function.json读取范围，从ISAPI读取当前值）\nfunction loadDeviceImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    if (!deviceIp) return;\n    \n    if (typeof apiGet === 'undefined') {\n        console.error('[IMAGE] apiGet not defined');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    console.log('[IMAGE] Loading image params for:', deviceIp);\n    \n    // v6.14: 使用 async/await 确保顺序但不阻塞 UI\n    (async function() {\n        try {\n            // 先加载 function.json\n            var r = await apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/function');\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n                deviceFunctionData = r.data;\n                console.log('[IMAGE] function.json loaded');\n            }\n        } catch (e) {\n            console.warn('[IMAGE] function.json failed:', e);\n        }\n        \n        // 然后加载其他参数（顺序执行但不阻塞）\n        loadExposure(deviceIp);\n        loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n        loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n        loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n        loadShutter(deviceIp);\n        loadIris(deviceIp);\n        loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n        loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    })();\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129814,"output":1452,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131266,"cost":{"input":0.12981399999999998,"output":0.0046464,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13446039999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781332870149,"responseId":"cht000df7b5@dx19ebfb68804ba5b442"}}
