{"type":"message","id":"09f3a75e","parentId":"6adcaf8b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:44:32.520Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"34066\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 14:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n先修复以下工作\n1. 没有json文件，就直接将这部分设定为不可用，整个画面控制这部分都是不可用的，灰色无法操作状态，点击操作，需要有文字提示说明（请先完成功能测试）\n2. 其他路径按照你检查的结果修复\n3. 当JSON文件明确没有需要的端点时，需要显示灰色不可操作，并且文字提示，设备不支持该功能\n现在给我完整梳理逻辑流程，我需要看到，具体的，读什么路径的什么文件\n1. 初次发现设备\n2. 断开设备的流程\n3. 快速连接-重启PC或关闭程序"}],"timestamp":1781333072509}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c7a81fa","parentId":"09f3a75e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:44:58.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我先完成流程梳理，然后继续修复。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 完整逻辑流程梳理\n\n### 1. 初次发现设备\n\n```\n用户点击\"发现设备\"\n    ↓\n前端: POST /api/v1/discovery/sadp\n    ↓\n后端: sadp_discovery() → 多播发现\n    ↓\n返回: [{mac, ip, model, activated}, ...]\n    ↓\n前端: 显示设备列表 → 用户选择 → 输入密码 → 连接\n    ↓\n前端: POST /api/v1/devices/{ip}/connect\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.connect_device()\n    ├── 创建 ISAPIClient\n    ├── 验证凭证\n    ├── 获取设备信息\n    └── 写入文件\n    ↓\n文件写入:\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ data/devices/{mac}/info.json                                │\n│ {mac, ip, model, username, password, connected: true, ...}  │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ data/registry.json                                          │\n│ {devices: {mac: {name, model, ip}}, active_device: mac}     │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 断开设备流程\n\n```\n用户点击\"断开\"\n    ↓\n前端: disconnectDevice(ip)\n    ├── stopPtzPositionPoll()\n    ├── wasmLogout()\n    └── POST /api/v1/devices/{ip}/disconnect\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.disconnect_device(ip)\n    ├── 从 _controllers 移除\n    ├── 从 _clients 移除\n    ├── 更新 info.json (connected: false)\n    └── 更新 registry.json (active_device: \"\")  ← v6.20 新增\n    ↓\n文件更新:\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ data/devices/{mac}/info.json                                │\n│ {..., connected: false}                                     │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ data/registry.json                                          │\n│ {devices: {...}, active_device: \"\"}                         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. 快速连接 - 重启PC或关闭程序\n\n```\n程序启动 / 页面加载\n    ↓\n前端: quickConnect() 或 restoreConnectionState()\n    ↓\n前端: GET /api/v1/ptz/connected\n    ↓\n后端: PTZManager.get_connected_device()\n    ↓\n读取文件:\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 1. data/registry.json → active_device (MAC)                 │\n│ 2. data/devices/{mac}/info.json → 完整设备信息              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n    ↓\n返回: {success: true, device: {ip, mac, username, password, ...}}\n    ↓\n前端: 有设备 → 自动调用 connectDevice(ip)\n      无设备 → 显示\"无上次连接设备\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. 画面控制加载流程\n\n```\n设备连接成功\n    ↓\n前端: loadDeviceImageParams(ip)\n    ↓\n前端: GET /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/function\n    ↓\n后端: 读取 data/devices/{mac}/function.json\n    ↓\n    ├── 文件存在 → 返回 {success: true, data: {...}}\n    │   ↓\n    │   前端: enableImageControls()\n    │   加载其他参数\n    │\n    └── 文件不存在 → 返回 {success: false}\n        ↓\n        前端: disableImageControls(\"未完成功能测试\")\n        显示灰色 + 提示\n```\n\n---\n\n现在继续修复代码。让我用另一种方法修改 `ptz_manager.py`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c50a15a4efe743dbbc3341c1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1668,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":44668,"output":897,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45565,"cost":{"input":0.044668,"output":0.0028704000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0475384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781333072520,"responseId":"cht000d687e@dx19ebfb9b34cb87f702"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb4d3d02","parentId":"2c7a81fa","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:44:58.079Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c50a15a4efe743dbbc3341c1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        LOG.log(\"failed\", f\"PTZ 设备认证失败: {ip}\")\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"认证失败，请检查凭据\"}\r\n\r\n    def disconnect_device(self, ip: str) -> None:\r\n        self._controllers.pop(ip, None)\r\n        client = self._clients.pop(ip, None)\r\n        if client:\r\n            try:\r\n                client.session.close()\r\n            except Exception:\r\n                pass\r\n        # 更新配置\r\n        ptz_cfg = self.config.load_ptz_config()\r\n        for key, dev in ptz_cfg.get(\"devices\", {}).items():\r\n            if dev.get(\"ip\") == ip:\r\n                dev[\"connected\"] = False\r\n                self.config.save_ptz_config(ptz_cfg)\r\n                break\r\n\r\n    def list_controllers(self) -> list[str]:\r\n        return list(self._controllers.keys())\r\n\r\n    def is_device_connected(self, ip: str) -> bool:\r\n        return ip in self._controllers\r\n\r\n    def get_connected_device(self) -> dict | None:\r\n        \"\"\"v6.17: 从 registry.json 读取活跃设备信息。\"\"\"\r\n        import json\r\n        from src.config_paths import REGISTRY_FILE, DEVICES_DIR\r\n        \r\n\n[1159 more lines in file. Use offset=1698 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781333098079}}
