{"type":"message","id":"fe2f3c8a","parentId":"821c9cd1","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:46:27.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.20 修复完成\n\n### 修改汇总\n\n| 文件 | 修改内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| `console.html` | 添加 `disableImageControls()` / `enableImageControls()` - 无 function.json 时画面控制灰色不可用 + 提示文字 |\n| `router.py` | 修复 `/ptz/{ip}/function` - 正确读取 `data/devices/{mac}/function.json` |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | 断开设备时清除 `registry.json` 的 `active_device` |\n| `index.html` | 版本号 v6.19 → v6.20 |\n\n---\n\n### 完整逻辑流程\n\n#### 1. 初次发现设备\n```\n发现设备 → 连接 → 写入:\n  - data/devices/{mac}/info.json (设备详情)\n  - data/registry.json (active_device: mac)\n```\n\n#### 2. 断开设备\n```\n断开 → 更新:\n  - info.json (connected: false)\n  - registry.json (active_device: \"\")\n```\n\n#### 3. 快速连接\n```\n启动 → GET /api/v1/ptz/connected\n  → 读取 registry.json → active_device\n  → 读取 data/devices/{mac}/info.json\n  → 自动连接\n```\n\n#### 4. 画面控制\n```\n连接成功 → GET /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/function\n  → 读取 data/devices/{mac}/function.json\n  → 存在: 启用控件\n  → 不存在: 禁用控件 + 提示\"未完成功能测试\"\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49328,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49681,"cost":{"input":0.049328,"output":0.0011296000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0504576}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781333176663,"responseId":"cht000d2386@dx19ebfbb3a4fb85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"37ee8e1e","parentId":"fe2f3c8a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:47:38.969Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"34090\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 14:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n重新快速连接，要读取 registry.json → active_device (MAC)。这个文件，在上次断开已经清理了，也就是说，你下次快速连接，永远无法读取正确的文件，永远是空文件，是这样吗？\n如果是，应该怎么修复，给我文字"}],"timestamp":1781333258965}}
{"type":"message","id":"51015025","parentId":"37ee8e1e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:47:51.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对！这是一个**逻辑矛盾**：\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 问题分析\n\n### 当前逻辑\n```\n断开设备 → registry.json.active_device = \"\"\n重启程序 → 快速连接 → 读取 registry.json.active_device → 空 → 无法自动连接\n```\n\n### 问题\n**断开 ≠ 忘记设备**。用户断开只是断开当前会话，不是要\"忘记\"这个设备。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 正确逻辑\n\n### 方案 A：断开不清除 active_device（推荐）\n```\n断开设备 → 只更新 info.json (connected: false)\n         → registry.json.active_device 保持不变\n\n重启程序 → 读取 registry.json.active_device → 有值\n         → 自动连接该设备\n```\n\n**理由**：\n- 用户断开只是暂时断开，下次启动还想连同一个设备\n- 如果要\"忘记设备\"，应该在设备管理里删除设备\n\n### 方案 B：断开时保存 \"last_connected\" 而非 \"active\"\n```\n断开设备 → registry.json.last_connected = mac（不清除）\n         → registry.json.active_device = \"\"\n\n重启程序 → 优先读 active_device，为空则读 last_connected\n         → 自动连接 last_connected\n```\n\n---\n\n## 推荐：方案 A\n\n**撤销刚才的修改**，断开设备时**不清除** `registry.json.active_device`。\n\n需要我修复吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49886,"output":292,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50178,"cost":{"input":0.049886,"output":0.0009344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0508204}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781333258969,"responseId":"cht000e2c19@dx19ebfbc7af8b893102"}}
