{"type":"message","id":"a1571506","parentId":"7808b4a3","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:59:07.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在完整理解了 `active_device` 的使用场景：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 `active_device` 使用场景分析\n\n### 当前源码中的使用\n\n| 文件 | 函数 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `router.py` | `GET /devices/active` | 获取当前活跃设备 |\n| `router.py` | `POST /devices/active` | 设置活跃设备（切换设备） |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `save_ptz_config()` | 保存时设置 `active_device` |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `upsert_device()` | 连接成功时设置 `active_device` |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `remove_device()` | 删除设备时清除 `active_device` |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `get_connected_device()` | **快速连接时读取** |\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `disconnect_device()` | **v6.20 错误地清除** |\n| `store.py` | `set_active_device()` | 设置活跃设备 |\n| `store.py` | `get_active_device()` | 获取活跃设备 |\n\n### 问题总结\n\n`active_device` 有**两种语义混淆**：\n\n1. **\"当前正在连接的设备\"** - 运行时状态\n2. **\"上次连接过的设备\"** - 用于快速连接恢复\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 修复方案：统一使用 `last_connected`\n\n### 修改内容\n\n| 操作 | 当前行为 | 修复后 |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| 连接成功 | `active_device = mac` | `last_connected = mac` |\n| 断开设备 | `active_device = \"\"` | **不变**（保留） |\n| 删除设备 | 清除 | 清除 |\n| 快速连接 | 读 `active_device` | 读 `last_connected` |\n| `GET /devices/active` | 读 `active_device` | 读 `last_connected` |\n\n### 字段重命名\n\n`active_device` → `last_connected`\n\n---\n\n开始实施修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14fa9dffea904d0b9fdadfe9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nv6.30: 将 active_device 重命名为 last_connected\n\"\"\"\nimport re\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 需要修改的文件\nfiles = [\n    Path(\"src/core/ptz_manager.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/storage/store.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/api/router.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/core/device_manager.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/core/startup.py\"),\n]\n\nfor file_path in files:\n    full_path = Path(\"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub\") / file_path\n    if not full_path.exists():\n        print(f\"SKIP: {file_path}\")\n        continue\n    \n    content = full_path.read_text(encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    # 替换字段名\n    content = content.replace('\"active_device\"', '\"last_connected\"')\n    content = content.replace(\"'active_device'\", \"'last_connected'\")\n    content = content.replace(\"active_device =\", \"last_connected =\")\n    content = content.replace(\"active_device=\", \"last_connected=\")\n    content = content.replace(\".get('active_device')\", \".get('last_connected')\")\n    content = content.replace('.get(\"active_device\")', '.get(\"last_connected\")')\n    \n    # 函数名也需要修改\n    content = content.replace(\"def get_active_device\", \"def get_last_connected_device\")\n    content = content.replace(\"def set_active_device\", \"def set_last_connected_device\")\n    content = content.replace(\"get_active_device(\", \"get_last_connected_device(\")\n    content = content.replace(\"set_active_device(\", \"set_last_connected_device(\")\n    \n    full_path.write_text(content, encoding='utf-8')\n    print(f\"OK: {file_path}\")\n\nprint(\"\\nDone!\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\rename_field.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":61885,"output":825,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62710,"cost":{"input":0.061884999999999996,"output":0.0026400000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.064525}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781333924071,"responseId":"cht000dee83@dx19ebfc6ab5bba5d322"}}
