{"type":"message","id":"ac185842","parentId":"a0959f28","timestamp":"2026-06-13T07:02:53.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.30 修复完成\n\n### 修改汇总\n\n| 文件 | 修改内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| `ptz_manager.py` | `active_device` → `last_connected`；`disconnect_device` 不清理 `last_connected` |\n| `store.py` | `active_device` → `last_connected` |\n| `router.py` | `active_device` → `last_connected`；API 注释更新 |\n| `device_manager.py` | `active_device` → `last_connected` |\n| `startup.py` | `active_device` → `last_connected` |\n| `index.html` | 版本号 v6.20 → v6.30 |\n\n---\n\n### 正确逻辑流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ registry.json                                                │\n│ { devices: {...}, last_connected: \"mac_A\" }                  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n连接成功 → last_connected = mac\n断开设备 → 不清理 last_connected（保留）\n删除设备 → 清理 last_connected（如果是该设备）\n快速连接 → 读 last_connected → 自动连接\n```\n\n---\n\n### E2E 测试流程\n\n1. **发现设备 → 连接** → `registry.json.last_connected = mac`\n2. **断开设备** → `registry.json.last_connected` 保持不变\n3. **重启程序 → 快速连接** → 读取 `last_connected` → 自动连接\n\n**准备 E2E 测试。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":64768,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65094,"cost":{"input":0.06476799999999999,"output":0.0010432,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06581119999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781334119370,"responseId":"cht000dc5fb@dx19ebfca18d6b91a742"}}
