{"type":"message","id":"b8697bfe","parentId":"7f0ff9f2","timestamp":"2026-06-13T07:20:24.957Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对！我理解错了。\n\n**问题**：我只改了名字，没有增加新字段。`active_device` 和 `last_connected` 是**两个不同的功能**，不是改名就能解决的。\n\n---\n\n## 正确理解\n\n| 字段 | 用途 | 何时更新 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| `active_device` | **当前正在连接的设备** | 连接成功 → 设置；断开 → 清空 |\n| `last_connected` | **上次连接过的设备** | 连接成功 → 设置；断开 → **保留** |\n\n---\n\n## 修复方案\n\n1. **恢复 `active_device`** - 保持原有逻辑\n2. **新增 `last_connected`** - 只在连接成功时设置，断开不清空\n\n开始修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_74fd22a96a214097b99f5bf5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nv6.30 修复: 恢复 active_device，新增 last_connected\n\"\"\"\nimport re\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nfiles = [\n    Path(\"src/core/ptz_manager.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/storage/store.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/api/router.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/core/device_manager.py\"),\n    Path(\"src/core/startup.py\"),\n]\n\nfor file_path in files:\n    full_path = Path(\"C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/agents/dev-factory/astrohub\") / file_path\n    if not full_path.exists():\n        print(f\"SKIP: {file_path}\")\n        continue\n    \n    content = full_path.read_text(encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    # 恢复 active_device 函数名\n    content = content.replace(\"def get_last_connected_device\", \"def get_active_device\")\n    content = content.replace(\"def set_last_connected_device\", \"def set_active_device\")\n    content = content.replace(\"get_last_connected_device(\", \"get_active_device(\")\n    content = content.replace(\"set_last_connected_device(\", \"set_active_device(\")\n    \n    full_path.write_text(content, encoding='utf-8')\n    print(f\"OK: {file_path}\")\n\nprint(\"\\nDone!\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\restore_active.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":67389,"output":454,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67843,"cost":{"input":0.067388999999