{"type":"message","id":"0e9e724e","parentId":"1615e67c","timestamp":"2026-06-13T07:23:23.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-501d7c0856644f1cbe88c72bb2bd3c05","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-13 15:25\n**状态**: v6.31 active_device + last_connected 双字段\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.31 修复内容\n| # | 修改项 | 说明 |\n|---|--------|------|\n| 1 | 恢复 active_device | 当前正在连接的设备 |\n| 2 | 新增 last_connected | 上次连接过的设备（断开保留） |\n| 3 | disconnect_device 只清 active_device | last_connected 保留用于快速连接 |\n\n### registry.json 结构\n```json\n{\n  \"devices\": { \"mac_A\": {...}, \"mac_B\": {...} },\n  \"active_device\": \"\",           // 当前连接的设备（连上有值，断开清空）\n  \"last_connected\": \"mac_A\"      // 上次连接的设备（断开保留）\n}\n```\n\n### 操作逻辑\n| 操作 | active_device | last_connected |\n|------|----------------|----------------|\n| 连接成功 | = mac | = mac |\n| 断开设备 | = \"\" | **保留** |\n| 删除设备 | = \"\" | = \"\"（如果是该设备） |\n| 快速连接 | 读 last_connected | |\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260613_143000/","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":69094,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69435,"cost":{"input":0.069094,"output":0.0010912,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0701852}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781335384216,"responseId":"cht000db67d@dx19ebfdcf57fba5e412"}}
