{"type":"message","id":"78373679","parentId":"92ee2261","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:36:30.080Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ Web 页面可以访问了！\n\n**现在老板可以打开 http://127.0.0.1:10280 或 http://localhost:10280**\n\n---\n\n## 🏭 问题原因\n\n之前我用 `--port 8000` 启动服务，但默认端口是 **10280**。老板访问的是 10280，自然无法打开。\n\n### 正确启动方式\n\n```bash\npython src/main.py --headless          # 使用默认端口 10280\npython src/main.py --headless --port 8000  # 使用自定义端口 8000\n```\n\n**服务已在 http://127.0.0.1:10280 运行。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":97374,"output":144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97518,"cost":{"input":0.097374,"output":0.00046080000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0978348}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781339777789,"responseId":"cht000db9f1@dx19ec01fffffba5b442"}}
