{"type":"message","id":"e88ea91f","parentId":"62ee8b63","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:46:32.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_20ab17566bc643f4a9f7b51c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ================================================================ #\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/function\", summary=\"获取设备function.json\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_device_function(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"v6.20: 从 data/devices/{mac}/function.json 读取设备功能参数范围。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from pathlib import Path\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\", \"data\": None}\r\n    \r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\", \"data\": None}\r\n    \r\n    # v6.20: 使用正确的路径 data/devices/{mac}/function.json\r\n    from src.advanced.device_path import get_devices_dir\r\n    devices_dir = get_devices_dir()\r\n    \r\n    # 遍历所有设备目录查找 function.json\r\n    for device_dir in devices_dir.iterdir():\r\n        if device_dir.is_dir():\r\n            # 检查 info.json 中的 IP 是否匹配\r\n            info_file = device_dir / \"info.json\"\r\n            if info_file.exists():\r\n                try:\r\n                    info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                    if info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\r\n                        # IP 匹配，读取 function.json\r\n                        func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                        if func_file.exists():\r\n                            func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                            return {\"success\": True, \"data\": func_data}\r\n                        else:\r\n                            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"未找到 function.json，请先完成功能测试\", \"data\": None}\r\n                except Exception as e:\r\n                    continue\r\n    \r\n    return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"未找到该设备的设备目录\", \"data\": None}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"获取白平衡设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_whitebalance(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备白平衡当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n\n[589 more lines in file. Use offset=2575 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781340392071}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca4d6e09","parentId":"e88ea91f","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:46:43.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在检查 WASM 视频流相关代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8d0c9f00aa4149929dfc2f4eddf7fd97","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\doc\\wasm_video_stream.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":103883,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103927,"cost":{"input":0.10388299999999999,"output":0.0001408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10402379999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781340392074,"responseId":"cht000d8e6c@dx19ec0295c7db958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6903aeac","parentId":"ca4d6e09","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:46:43.671Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-8d0c9f00aa4149929dfc2f4eddf7fd97","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# WASM SDK 视频流实现方法\n\n**日期**: 2026-05-22\n**摄像头**: 海康威视 iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A (192.168.5.72)\n**WebSocket 端口**: 7681\n\n---\n\n## 一、整体流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    WASM SDK 视频流流程                           │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  用户点击连接                                                    │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  WASM SDK I_Login (登录)                                        │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  获取 WebSession cookie                                         │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  延迟 500ms                                                      │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  I_GetDevicePort (获取 WebSocket 端口)                          │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  getChannelInfo (获取通道信息)                                  │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  ISAPI/Security/token (获取 szAuth)                             │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  WebSocket 连接 (带 token + WebSession cookie)                  │\n│      ↓                                                          │\n│  视频流播放                                                      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、关键顺序（必须严格遵守）\n\n### 2.1 登录流程\n\n```javascript\n// 1. 用户点击连接设备\nclickLogin2()\n\n// 2. SDK 登录\nWebVideoCtrl.I_Login(szIP, 1, szPort, szUsername, szPassword, {\n    success: function(xmlDoc) {\n        // 3. 延迟 500ms（必须）\n        setTimeout(() => {\n            // 4. 获取端口\n            var oPort = WebVideoCtrl.I_GetDevicePort(g_szDeviceIdentify2);\n            \n            // 5. 获取通道（Promise）\n            getChannelInfo().then(() => {\n                // 6. 开始播放\n                clickStartRealPlay({ iStreamType: 2 });\n            });\n        }, 500);\n    }\n});\n```\n\n### 2.2 getChannelInfo 实现（返回 Promise）\n\n```javascript\nfunction getChannelInfo() {\n    return new Promise((resolve) => {\n        WebVideoCtrl.I_GetAnalogChannelInfo(szDeviceIdentify, {\n            async: true,\n            success: function(xmlDoc) {\n                // 解析通道\n                resolve();\n            },\n            error: function(status) {\n                resolve(); // 失败也继续\n            }\n        });\n    });\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、WebSocket URL 格式\n\nSDK 发送的 WebSocket URL 格式：\n\n```\nws://proxy_host:proxy_port/?version=0.1&cipherSuites=0&token=<szAuth>\n```\n\n**关键点**：\n- URL 路径是 `/`（根路径），不是 `/ws`\n- token 来自 `/ISAPI/Security/token` API\n- 需要 WebSession cookie 认证\n\n---\n\n## 四、代理路由配置\n\n### 4.1 WebSocket 代理路由\n\n```python\n# 处理所有 WebSocket 路径\napp.add_websocket_route(\"/ws\", ws_handler)\napp.add_websocket_route(\"/\", ws_handler)\napp.add_websocket_route(\"/{path:path}\", ws_handler)\n```\n\n### 4.2 WebSocket handler 核心逻辑\n\n```python\nasync def ws_handler(websocket: WebSocket):\n    # 1. 获取 token\n    token = websocket.query_params.get(\"token\", \"\")\n    if not token:\n        # 无 token = 健康检查，关闭连接\n        await websocket.accept()\n        await websocket.close()\n        return\n    \n    # 2. 从 cookie 获取摄像头 IP 和端口\n    ws_cookie = websocket.headers.get(\"cookie\", \"\")\n    camera_ip = \"192.168.5.72\"\n    camera_ws_port = 7681\n    \n    for cookie in ws_cookie.split(\";\"):\n        if cookie.startswith(\"webVideoCtrlProxyWs=\"):\n            target = cookie.split(\"=\")[1]\n            parts = target.split(\":\")\n            camera_ip = parts[0]\n            camera_ws_port = int(parts[1])\n    \n    # 3. 获取 WebSession cookie\n    ws_session_cookie = \"\"\n    for c in ws_cookie.split(\";\"):\n        if c.startswith(\"WebSession\"):\n            ws_session_cookie = c\n    \n    # 4. 构建摄像头 WebSocket URL\n    camera_ws_url = f\"ws://{camera_ip}:{camera_ws_port}/101?version=0.1&cipherSuites=0&token={token}\"\n    \n    # 5. 连接摄像头\n    ws_auth_headers = {\"Cookie\": ws_session_cookie}\n    async with websockets.connect(camera_ws_url, additional_headers=ws_auth_headers) as cam_ws:\n        # 双向转发消息\n        await asyncio.gather(\n            browser_to_camera(),\n            camera_to_browser()\n        )\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、ISAPI 代理配置\n\n### 5.1 sessionLogin 处理\n\n```python\n# 登录成功后自动获取 szAuth\nif 'sessionLogin' in path and request.method == 'POST':\n    # 1. 转发登录请求\n    # 2. 获取 WebSession cookie\n    # 3. 获取 szAuth from /ISAPI/Security/token\n    # 4. 添加 X-SZAuth header 到响应\n```\n\n### 5.2 System/capabilities 处理\n\n```python\n# 返回 WebSocket 支持标志\nif 'System/capabilities' in path:\n    return '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<DeviceCap version=\"2.0\">\n    <NetworkCap>\n        <isSupportWebsocket>true</isSupportWebsocket>\n    </NetworkCap>\n</DeviceCap>'''\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、错误修复记录\n\n### 6.1 变量名错误\n\n```python\n# 错误：\ntoken_url = f\"http://{camera_ip}:{port}/ISAPI/Security/token...\"\n\n# 正确：\ntoken_url = f\"http://{camera_ip}:{camera_port}/ISAPI/Security/token...\"\n```\n\n### 6.2 WebSocket 路由覆盖\n\nSDK 发送 `/?version=...&token=xxx`，必须处理所有路径。\n\n### 6.3 不手动获取 szAuth\n\n**重要**：博客方案的核心是让 SDK 自己处理认证，不手动干预。\n\n---\n\n## 七、关键 Cookie\n\n| Cookie 名称 | 来源 | 用途 |\n|------------|------|------|\n| WebSession_15edb5a7ff | sessionLogin | ISAPI 认证 |\n| webVideoCtrlProxyWs | 前端设置 | 摄像机地址:端口 |\n| token (query param) | SDK 获取 | WebSocket 认证 |\n\n---\n\n## 八、端口说明\n\n| 端口 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| 80 | ISAPI HTTP API |\n| 7681 | WebSocket 视频流（需认证） |\n| 7682 | 非 WebSocket 端口 |\n| 10280 | 本代理端口 |\n\n---\n\n## 九、参考资源\n\n- 博客文章: https://www.scaugreen.cn/posts/20990/\n- 海康 WASM SDK: webVideoCtrl.js"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781340403671}}
