t_device 只清 active_device | last_connected 保留用于快速连接 |\n\n### registry.json 结构\n```json\n{\n  \"devices\": { \"mac_A\": {...}, \"mac_B\": {...} },\n  \"active_device\": \"\",           // 当前连接的设备（连上有值，断开清空）\n  \"last_connected\": \"mac_A\"      // 上次连接的设备（断开保留）\n}\n```\n\n### 操作逻辑\n| 操作 | active_device | last_connected |\n|------|----------------|----------------|\n| 连接成功 | = mac | = mac |\n| 断开设备 | = \"\" | **保留** |\n| 删除设备 | = \"\" | = \"\"（如果是该设备） |\n| 快速连接 | 读 last_connected | |\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260613_143000/"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781340529023}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bb129b9","parentId":"a39456bc","timestamp":"2026-06-13T08:49:21.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"时间不够了。让我先记录关键信息给老板：\n\n---\n\n## 🏭 v6.33 问题排查报告\n\n### 问题清单\n\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | WASM 视频流无法播放 | 需对比 6.1x 版本差异 |\n| 2 | 画面控制显示\"未完成功能测试\" | **原因明确：无 function.json** |\n| 3 | 硬编码 IP | `src/main/main.py` 有 `192.168.5.72` |\n\n### 文件规范 (data_storage.md)\n\n正确路径：\n```\ndata/devices/{mac}/info.json       # 设备信息\ndata/devices/{mac}/function.json   # 功能探测结果 ← 缺失！\ndata/registry.json                 # last_connected\n```\n\n### 当前设备目录\n\n```\ndata/devices/240f9b764193/\n├── info.json  ✓\n└── function.json ✗ 缺失\n```\n\n### 解决方案\n\n**画面控制问题**：\n- API 已正确读取 `data/devices/{mac}/function.json`\n- 但该设备没有功能测试数据，所以显示\"未完成功能测试\"是**正确行为**\n- 需要先运行功能探测才会生成 `function.json`\n\n**WASM 问题**：\n- 需对比 6.1x 版本和当前版本差异\n\n**时间不足，需要下次继续排查 WASM 和硬编码问题。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":139307,"output":316,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139623,"cost":{"input":0.139307,"output":0.0010112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14031819999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781340529026,"responseId":"cht000d3882@dx19ec02b8c0fb894142"}}
