{"type":"message","id":"75f90fb7","parentId":"b1b643a2","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:13:27.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API 正确返回\"未找到功能探测数据\"。这是预期行为——设备确实没有 function.json。\n\n---\n\n## 🏭 v6.33 修复完成\n\n### 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | API 只读 `function.json` | 改用 `get_data_path_read()` 支持时间戳文件 |\n| 2 | 路径规范 | 按文档规范：`data/devices/{mac}/function.json` 或 `function_*.json` |\n\n### 文件规范（按文档）\n\n```\ndata/devices/{mac}/\n├── info.json           # 设备信息\n├── function.json       # 功能探测（或 function_*.json）\n├── limit.json          # 限位测试（或 limit_*.json）\n└── speed.json          # 速度测试（或 speed_*.json）\n```\n\n### E2E 测试结果\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| Web 页面 | ✅ 200 OK |\n| API 健康检查 | ✅ healthy |\n| function API | ✅ 正确返回\"未找到功能探测数据\" |\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.33\n\n**服务运行在 http://127.0.0.1:10280**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":142313,"output":283,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142596,"cost":{"input":0.142313,"output":0.0009056000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1432186}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781341994260,"responseId":"cht000d7359@dx19ec041c910b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"72a18443","parentId":"75f90fb7","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:13:35.536Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-13 17:11:13 GMT+8] Exec failed (tide-lob, signal SIGKILL) :: , stripped=System/deviceInfo, has_body=False INFO: 127.0.0.1:28811 - \"GET /ISAPI/System/deviceInfo HTTP/1.1\" 401 Unauthorized INFO: 127.0.0.1:36185 - \"GET /api/v1/devices HTTP/1.1…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-06-13 17:11:37 GMT+8] Exec completed (neat-oce, code 1) :: ����̽�ⱨ�� #1/3 [SADP] SendInquiry �ѷ��� [SADP] �ص��¼�: ADD, MAC=24-0f-9b-76-41-93, IP=192.168.5.72 [SADP] �ص��¼�: UPDATE, MAC=24-0f-9b-76-41-93, IP=192.168.5.72 [SADP] ����̽�ⱨ�� #…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"34236\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-06-13 17:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n优先固定名称，其次最新时间戳\n修改逻辑，必须读最新的function、limit、speed这些json，而且，必须是mac匹配的，不能读错硬件对应的文档"}],"timestamp":1781342015530}}
{"type":"message","id":"069b5482","parentId":"72a18443","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:13:43.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，修改逻辑：\n1. **优先最新时间戳文件，其次固定名称**\n2. **必须 MAC 匹配，不能读错设备的数据**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-4b86938d41004c0eb2e51582acd54c5b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129525,"output":66,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129591,"cost":{"input":0.129525,"output":0.0002112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1297362}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781342015537,"responseId":"cht000d7710@dx19ec042144eb91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b3ff5b6","parentId":"069b5482","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:13:43.381Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-4b86938d41004c0eb2e51582acd54c5b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v2.0 - 设备数据路径管理\n\nv6.19 更新:\n- 删除 config_paths 依赖，统一路径定义\n- 统一路径：data/devices/{mac}/\n- 带时间戳文件：data/devices/{mac}/{test_type}_{timestamp}.json\n- 读取规则：永远读最新记录\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\n# ================================================================ #\n#  统一路径定义 (v6.19)\n# ================================================================ #\n\ndef _get_app_dir() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取应用程序根目录。\"\"\"\n    import sys\n    if getattr(sys, 'frozen', False):\n        return Path(sys.executable).parent\n    return Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent.parent\n\nAPP_DIR = _get_app_dir()\nDATA_DIR = APP_DIR / 'data'\nDEVICES_DIR = DATA_DIR / 'devices'\n\n\ndef get_devices_dir() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"v6.19: 获取设备数据根目录。\"\"\"\n    return DEVICES_DIR\n\n\ndef get_device_info(ptz: Any) -> dict[str, str]:\n    \"\"\"从设备获取唯一标识信息。\n\n    Args:\n        ptz: PTZController实例\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: {mac, model, model_short, serial}\n    \"\"\"\n    # 从PTZController获取ISAPIClient\n    client = ptz.client if hasattr(ptz, 'client') else ptz\n\n    # 获取设备信息\n    resp = client.get('/System/deviceInfo')\n    xml = resp.xml\n\n    # 解析XML\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    root = ET.fromstring(xml)\n\n    # 提取字段\n    mac = \"\"\n    model = \"\"\n    serial = \"\"\n\n    for child in root:\n        tag = child.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in child.tag else child.tag\n        if tag == 'macAddress':\n            mac = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'model':\n            model = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'serialNumber':\n            serial = child.text or \"\"\n\n    # MAC地址去除冒号，转小写\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(':', '').lower()\n\n    # 短型号：取前缀（去掉后缀数字和字母）\n    # iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A -> iDS-2DF8C\n    model_short = model\n    if len(model) > 8:\n        model_short = model[:8]\n        while model_short and model_short[-1].isdigit():\n            model_short = model_short[:-1]\n\n    return {\n        'mac': mac,\n        'mac_clean': mac_clean,\n        'model': model,\n        'model_short': model_short,\n        'serial': serial\n    }\n\n\ndef get_device_dir(mac_clean: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"v6.03: 获取设备数据目录路径。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: data/devices/{mac_clean}/\n    \"\"\"\n    return DEVICES_DIR / mac_clean\n\n\ndef get_data_path_read(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"v6.19: 获取读取路径（优先固定文件，其次最新时间戳文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号（可选，v6.19 不再使用）\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径，如不存在返回None\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(mac_clean)\n    if not device_dir.exists():\n        return None\n\n    # 优先查找固定名称文件\n    fixed_path = device_dir / f'{test_type}.json'\n    if fixed_path.exists():\n        return fixed_path\n\n    # 其次查找最新的 {test_type}_*.json 文件\n    pattern = re.compile(rf'^{test_type}_(\\d{{8}}_\\d{{6}})\\.json$')\n    latest_file = None\n    latest_time = None\n\n    for f in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if f.is_file():\n            match = pattern.match(f.name)\n            if match:\n                file_time = f.stat().st_mtime\n                if latest_time is None or file_time > latest_time:\n                    latest_time = file_time\n                    latest_file = f\n\n    return latest_file\n\n\ndef get_data_path_write(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"v6.19: 获取写入路径（固定名称文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号（可选，v6.19 不再使用）\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径 data/devices/{mac_clean}/{test_type}.json\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(mac_clean)\n    device_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    return device_dir / f'{test_type}.json'\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781342023381}}
{"type":"message","id":"416c257c","parentId":"9b3ff5b6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:14:05.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改 `get_data_path_read`：**优先最新时间戳，其次固定名称**："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d38efcaa6d7a413788945647","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def get_data_path_read(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"v6.33: 获取读取路径（优先最新时间戳文件，其次固定名称文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号（可选，v6.33 不再使用）\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）- 必须匹配设备\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径，如不存在返回None\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(mac_clean)\n    if not device_dir.exists():\n        return None\n\n    # v6.33: 优先查找最新的 {test_type}_*.json 时间戳文件\n    pattern = re.compile(rf'^{test_type}_(\\d{{8}}_\\d{{6}})\\.json$')\n    latest_file = None\n    latest_time = None\n\n    for f in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if f.is_file():\n            match = pattern.match(f.name)\n            if match:\n                file_time = f.stat().st_mtime\n                if latest_time is None or file_time > latest_time:\n                    latest_time = file_time\n                    latest_file = f\n\n    # 有时间戳文件则返回最新的\n    if latest_file:\n        return latest_file\n\n    # 其次查找固定名称文件\n    fixed_path = device_dir / f'{test_type}.json'\n    if fixed_path.exists():\n        return fixed_path\n\n    return None","oldText":"def get_data_path_read(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"v6.19: 获取读取路径（优先固定文件，其次最新时间戳文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号（可选，v6.19 不再使用）\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径，如不存在返回None\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(mac_clean)\n    if not device_dir.exists():\n        return None\n\n    # 优先查找固定名称文件\n    fixed_path = device_dir / f'{test_type}.json'\n    if fixed_path.exists():\n        return fixed_path\n\n    # 其次查找最新的 {test_type}_*.json 文件\n    pattern = re.compile(rf'^{test_type}_(\\d{{8}}_\\d{{6}})\\.json$')\n    latest_file = None\n    latest_time = None\n\n    for f in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if f.is_file():\n            match = pattern.match(f.name)\n            if match:\n                file_time = f.stat().st_mtime\n                if latest_time is None or file_time > latest_time:\n                    latest_time = file_time\n                    latest_file = f\n\n    return latest_file"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":140396,"output":764,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141160,"cost":{"input":0.140396,"output":0.0024448,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1428408}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781342023384,"responseId":"cht000d7811@dx19ec04232f6b894142"}}
