{"type":"message","id":"2d1c299a","parentId":"7232bf03","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:16:21.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.33 修复完成\n\n### 修复内容\n\n| # | 修改 | 说明 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | `get_data_path_read` | **优先最新时间戳文件，其次固定名称** |\n| 2 | API `/ptz/{ip}/function` | **必须通过 IP → MAC 匹配**，确保读正确设备的数据 |\n\n### 读取逻辑\n\n```\nget_data_path_read(mac_clean, test_type):\n    1. 查找 data/devices/{mac}/{test_type}_*.json（时间戳文件）\n    2. 返回最新的（按修改时间）\n    3. 没有时间戳文件 → 返回 {test_type}.json（固定名称）\n```\n\n### API 流程\n\n```\nGET /api/v1/ptz/{ip}/function\n    ↓\n1. IP → 解析 → 找到 MAC\n2. MAC → data/devices/{mac}/\n3. 读取 function.json 或 function_*.json（优先时间戳）\n4. MAC 不匹配 → 错误\n```\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.33\n\n**服务已在 http://127.0.0.1:10280 运行并测试通过。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":145131,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145400,"cost":{"input":0.14513099999999998,"output":0.0008608000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14599179999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781342168905,"responseId":"cht000deb46@dx19ec0446b11ba5d322"}}
