{"type":"message","id":"c2a2dee5","parentId":"1b8439a7","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:16:43.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"E2E 测试完成，服务已清理。\n\n---\n\n## 🏭 v6.33 总结\n\n### 修复内容\n\n| 文件 | 修改 |\n|------|------|\n| `device_path.py` | 读取逻辑：**优先最新时间戳文件，其次固定名称** |\n| `router.py` | API 必须通过 IP → MAC 匹配，确保读正确设备数据 |\n\n### 测试结果\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| Web 页面 | ✅ 200 OK |\n| API 健康检查 | ✅ healthy |\n| function API | ✅ 正确返回\"未找到功能探测数据\"（设备无数据） |\n\n### 文件规范\n\n```\ndata/devices/{mac}/\n├── info.json              # 设备信息\n├── function.json          # 功能探测（固定名称）\n├── function_*.json        # 功能探测（时间戳）← 优先读取最新的\n├── limit.json / limit_*.json\n└── speed.json / speed_*.json\n```\n\n**服务已在 http://127.0.0.1:10280 验证通过。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":145561,"output":252,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145813,"cost":{"input":0.145561,"output":0.0008064000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1463674}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781342188005,"responseId":"cht000df1be@dx19ec044b52fb87f702"}}
