{"type":"message","id":"dda0ff56","parentId":"ec5d15c0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T10:10:43.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.35 修复完成\n\n### 修改内容\n\n| 功能 | 修改 |\n|------|------|\n| 连接按钮 | **连接/断开按钮 → 开关样式** |\n| 信息按钮 | **信息按钮 → 弹窗显示设备详情** |\n| 状态同步 | `updateDeviceStatus` 刷新设备列表开关状态 |\n\n### 新增函数\n\n```javascript\ntoggleDeviceConnect(ip, checked)  // 切换设备连接状态\nshowDeviceInfoModal(ip)           // 弹窗显示设备信息\n```\n\n### 开关逻辑\n\n```\n设备列表开关：\n- 打开 → 连接该设备（断开其他设备）\n- 关闭 → 断开该设备\n- 同时只能有一个设备连接\n```\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.35\n\n**服务运行在 http://127.0.0.1:10280**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":57514,"output":191,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57705,"cost":{"input":0.057513999999999996,"output":0.0006112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.058125199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781345428630,"responseId":"cht000d40f5@dx19ec0764105b91a742"}}
