{"type":"message","id":"da6e0161","parentId":"509fb069","timestamp":"2026-06-13T10:10:57.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"服务已清理。\n\n---\n\n## 🏭 v6.35 总结\n\n### 修改内容\n\n| 功能 | 修改前 | 修改后 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 连接按钮 | \"连接\"/\"断开\" 两个按钮 | 开关样式，只能连接一个设备 |\n| 信息显示 | 内联显示 | 弹窗显示设备详情 |\n\n### 新增函数\n\n- `toggleDeviceConnect(ip, checked)` — 切换设备连接状态\n- `showDeviceInfoModal(ip)` — 弹窗显示设备信息\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.35"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":57790,"output":125,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57915,"cost":{"input":0.057789999999999994,"output":0.0004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05818999999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781345449141,"responseId":"cht000d558c@dx19ec0767a93ba5e412"}}
