{"type":"message","id":"14c90613","parentId":"42d9a7ee","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:57:29.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.36 修复完成\n\n### 问题\n\n**WASM 视频流无法播放**：静态文件路径错误\n\n### 根本原因\n\n静态文件挂载配置错误：\n- 挂载 `/static` → `src/web/`\n- 但静态文件在 `src/web/static/`\n- 导致访问 `/static/websdk/wasm/webVideoCtrl.js` 时实际路径是 `src/web/websdk/wasm/webVideoCtrl.js`（不存在）\n\n### 修复\n\n修改挂载路径：\n```python\n# 修复前\napp.mount(\"/static\", StaticFiles(directory=str(_WEB_DIR), html=True), name=\"static\")\n\n# 修复后\napp.mount(\"/static\", StaticFiles(directory=str(_WEB_DIR / \"static\"), html=True), name=\"static\")\n```\n\n### 测试结果\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| Web 页面 | ✅ 200 OK |\n| API 健康检查 | ✅ healthy |\n| WASM SDK 文件 | ✅ 200 OK |\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.36\n\n**服务运行在 http://127.0.0.1:10280**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":91690,"output":253,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91943,"cost":{"input":0.09169,"output":0.0008096000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09249959999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781359032128,"responseId":"cht000d4811@dx19ec145ca29b91a742"}}
