{"type":"message","id":"5e61b62f","parentId":"39728042","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:01:10.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_488c1527b3dc4994bc3b5c0f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-06-13 开发日志\n\n## v6.33\n- **修复**：`device_path.py` 读取逻辑改为优先最新时间戳文件，其次固定名称\n- **修复**：API `/ptz/{ip}/function` 必须通过 IP → MAC 匹配，确保读正确设备数据\n\n## v6.34\n- **问题**：页面加载时自动连接设备，但快速连接开关显示关闭，设备列表显示\"连接\"按钮\n- **修复**：初始化获取连接状态后调用 `updateDeviceStatus()` 同步 UI 状态\n\n## v6.35\n- **修改**：设备管理页面连接按钮改为开关样式，同时只能有一个设备连接\n- **新增**：`toggleDeviceConnect(ip, checked)` 切换设备连接状态\n- **新增**：`showDeviceInfoModal(ip)` 弹窗显示设备信息\n- **修复**：`updateDeviceStatus` 刷新设备列表开关状态\n\n## v6.36\n- **问题**：WASM 视频流无法播放，所有静态文件返回 404\n- **根本原因**：静态文件挂载路径错误\n  - 挂载 `/static` → `src/web/`\n  - 实际静态文件在 `src/web/static/`\n- **修复**：`main.py` 第 253 行\n  ```python\n  app.mount(\"/static\", StaticFiles(directory=str(_WEB_DIR / \"static\"), html=True), name=\"static\")\n  ```\n\n## 教训\n1. **静态文件挂载**：FastAPI `StaticFiles` 挂载时，路径必须精确指向静态文件所在目录，而不是其父目录\n2. **UI 状态同步**：初始化完成后必须调用状态更新函数同步 UI\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-06-13.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":47848,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48272,"cost":{"input":0.047847999999999995,"output":0.0013568,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04920479999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781359249352,"responseId":"cht000dc3f6@dx19ec149172fba5d322"}}
