{"type":"message","id":"369381bf","parentId":"7225186c","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:12:00.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🏭 v6.37 修复完成\n\n### 问题\n\nWASM 视频流播放失败，Decoder.wasm 文件返回 404\n\n### 根本原因\n\n1. **静态文件挂载路径错误**（v6.36 已修复）\n2. **WASM SDK 未设置 `szBasePath`**，导致 WASM 文件路径不正确\n\n### 修复\n\n1. `main.py`：静态文件挂载路径修正为 `_WEB_DIR / \"static\"`\n2. `index.html`：添加 `szBasePath: \"/static/websdk/wasm\"` 配置\n\n### 测试结果\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| 服务健康检查 | ✅ healthy |\n| WASM SDK 文件 | ✅ 200 OK |\n| Decoder.wasm 文件 | ✅ 200 OK |\n\n### 版本号\n\nv6.37\n\n**老板请打开 http://127.0.0.1:10280 测试 WASM 视频流是否正常播放。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":130254,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130478,"cost":{"input":0.13025399999999998,"output":0.0007168000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13097079999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781359908719,"responseId":"cht000ecb7a@dx19ec1531d02b893102"}}
